===Glyph origin===
{{Han etym}}

{{Han compound|又|厂|ls=psc|c1=s|c2=p|t1=hand}}. The character originally depicted the action of turning the palm of the hand, and by extension, it came to mean "to return" or "to reverse."<ref>Digital Shinjigen 2017</ref>

