===Etymology 1===
{{zh-forms|alt=仮}}
STEDT compares it to {{inh|zh|sit-pro|*par||to trade; to buy; to sell}}, from which {{cog|bo|ཕར||interest (on money); exchange}} is derived.

Cognate with {{och-l|販|to trade}}, which is an exoactive of {{och-l|反|to return, ''lit.'' to make someone return}} ({{zh-ref|Schuessler, 2007}}).

{{och-l|番|a turn; a time|id=4}} is the iterative of {{och-l|反}}.

